features.text:
#HappyMan
by Eric Stow

Stow's meta graphic novel/comic book series follows the adventures of HappyMan as he navigates his self-created universe on a quest to Worthy.

HappyMan begins his journey in a sketch pad, encountering surreal sidekicks and meta monsters on his quest to worthy. As he learns to create his own universe, he transitions to a rich, hi-res digital landscape, discovering new superpowers and upgrades along the way.

features.text:
# Welcome to the Future of Book Publishing on Web 3.0
WIP Publishing is re-envisioning how authors produce, distribute, and monetize their creative works in new, exciting ways that directly connects them with their readers through #NFTBooks.

#The Millenial Mentality
by Elan M. Carson

Millennials have heard all of the cultural criticisms and backlash; we are bemoaned a generation of entitlement and nicknamed monikers such as Gen Why?, Internet Generation, MyPod Generation, and the Boomerang Generation.

# Bring Back Satire
by Thomas Dylan Daniel

The making of Bring Back Satire started in January, 2020. I was newly engaged with the Cent platform, and made the executive decision to allow it to impact the book. I published essays, poems, and short stories together in one volume. Viva Variety!

Here we are, 15 months later. Instead of a simple book, Bring Back Satire is now the vehicle I've used to figure out how to mint books to the blockchain.

I've even founded the Libernet DAO to ensure that blockchain protocols can be cost-effectively used to allow authors everywhere to earn a much higher portion of the proceeds generated by their work.

We'll just mint our books to the blockchain, then they'll be available everywhere.
Send your WAX NFTs to wall.gems & we will put it up here

# Instructions

How to get the full experience:

|  |    |
| ----------- |:---------:|
| 1.          | Click the Video Screen to watch the HotSauce Live Show |      |
| 2.          | Click Discord Logo on your right side and join Audio Chat |
| 3.          | Register and get whitelisted for the "Race for Rares" Token Drop on the Parcel  ( look behind the bar )    |
| 4.          | Click on the Spicy Rare image and claim your free NFT on AtomicHub|
Spit raps. mint tracks. sell for digital cash.
